    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 5. CFD-predicted NIH values are within acceptable agreement with bench measurements across the CPB operating envelope, and the relative hemolysis index RH is below 1.0 at all operating points. The hemolysis damage model form is corroborated by secondary validation data. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the decision that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for this Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
